<body>
  <h1>Orion Retail Group - Resource Plan</h1>
  <table><tr><th>Delivery Lead</th><td>New delivery lead joined in May and improved communication cadence.</td></tr>
<tr><th>Critical Dependency</th><td>Payment gateway specialist is a single point of dependency.</td></tr>
<tr><th>Backup Readiness</th><td>Backup engineer identified but has not completed checkout architecture onboarding.</td></tr>
<tr><th>Team Stability</th><td>Core squad is stable; two sprint commitments slipped because of gateway defects.</td></tr>
<tr><th>Resource Health</th><td>Moderate risk until specialist backup is fully ready.</td></tr></table>
